# wire backend

## how to run
with docker (debian has a tls bug -> docker solves this)

read build/alpine/README.md for initial compilation of docker dependencies

### if haskell code has changed
from wire-server dir:
```
sudo make docker-intermediate # recompiles haskell code, takes a while
```
```
sudo make docker-services # just cuts the intermediate image up
```
to start fake AWS:
```
sudo deploy/docker-ephemeral/run.sh
```

and finally to run wire-server:
```
sudo deploy/services-demo/demo.sh docker
```


